title: Mack and VY among former Longhorns on Fresh Ed Panel
text:
Mack and VY among former Longhorns on Fresh Ed Panel Mack and VY among former Longhorns on FreshEd Panel Post to Facebook Mack and VY among former Longhorns on Fresh Ed Panel Mack and VY among former Longhorns on FreshEd Panel  //kvue.tv/1RV5JRm   Mack and VY among former Longhorns on Fresh Ed Panel Shawn Clynch, KVUE 10:57 p.m. CDT October 20, 2015 
Former Longhorn tight end Bo Scaife brought the Fresh Ed experience to Austin. Bo Scaife's FreshEd for Area Youth KVUE 
It provides area youth who hope to experience the same as Scaife and other former Longhorns experienced during their time at UT. The program provides insight on achieving success in life in general. http://freshedlife.com/about-us/ 
Scaife was the moderator of tonight's event. The panel included Mack Brown, Vince Young, Ricky Williams, & Kasey Studdard. 
Click on the video player to see the story. Read or Share this story: http://kvue.tv/1RV5JRm TOP VIDEOS
